# Store project

The project is a website to buy sports shoes..
* Home Page 
* Sales Page 
* Profile Page

#### In this project I used:
- Column
- Row
- List view
- Conteiner
- Navigeter
- Bottom Navigation Bar
- Botton
- Image
- Grid View
- Sized Box
- ...etc
